# Other Ostomy Products

  1. Products
  2. Stoma
  3. Other Ostomy Products 

# Other Ostomy Products

Mediplast’s ostomy range can cater to non-standard stoma pouch requirements.
Utilising the same skin-friendly hydrocolloid technology and performance
design, we offer products for irrigation and continent stomas. We also offer
adaptable and drainable paediatric products which are extra gentle on the
skin. There are also accessories for dressing around a suprapubic catheter or
gastrostomy.

**Our productrange differs in our different markets. In order to see the
correct range of products, select desired "Market" at the top of the page.**
